{
  "stem": "9262.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I had the wisdom of Solomon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I knew it was really very difficult for the simple reason that once I was outside, in the middle of the town, it was not too bad.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I could buy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I could go in, in the butcher shop, and buy two kilos of bacon, or one kilo here, and one kilo in another shop, and carry it with me on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But getting back to the ghetto, where the Poles, on both sides of the road, sized up people going backwards and forwards, seeing their movements, looking at them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Do they look Jewish?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Do-- don't they-- don't they look Jewish?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Is there something-- are they hiding something, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So after that, I ceased.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I didn't go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I said-- on the whole, I think, I had only done three trips outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But you made the soap?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we made the soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even sold the soap myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now my cousin, who later on went to America after the war, he was very good in making the soap.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had the molds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had the know how and, of course, the fat-- which I supplied.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had the essences.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the soap, when it was fresh, had a very nice smell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We called it Lux Soap.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was green-- sometimes green, sometimes pink, and sometimes white and beige.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there were four colors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But when it was out in the sun too long, the soda would come out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, we had to choose another venue, to go into a different street, in order not to be recognized.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Otherwise, the people wanted to have their money back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So this went on for a little while, until the stock lasted.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
